ARM: tegra: Enable SGTL5000 audio

The NVIDIA Tegra 3 aka T30 based Apalis T30 and Colibri T30 as well as
the new Tegra K1 aka TK1 based Apalis TK1 modules contain a Freescale
SGTL5000 analogue audio codec.

